title: All for One
description: Pocoyo wants to play but Baby Bird is flying up in the sky, Pato and Octopus are helicoptering, Elly is jumping up into outer space and even little Caterpillar transforms into a butterfly and flutters away. Pocoyo feels left out so they get together to help him fly up in the sky along with them.

title: Sleepover
description: Bing & Coco are having a sleepover today! They mix up their bedtimes and Bing shows Coco his nightlight Owly. But what will happen when Coco turns all the lights out to show Bing what Amber, one of her Rainbow Fairy Mice, can do?

title: Transylbabies
description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

title: Portal hacia Helen
description: Craig hace una conexión a larga distancia con un niño que ama el Arroyo tanto como él.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: My Enemy, My Friend
description: The Ice Emperor's terrible Ice Dragon strikes again, laying waste to the Ice Fisher's village, forcing the ninja to go after Lloyd…

title: Not So Secret Service
description: After Mojo Jojo's latest creation threatens to blast him into tiny bits, the Powerpuff Girls are forced to take Mojo in.

title: #RageCat
description: Jessica Cruz is convinced she can find the purr-fect forever home for Dexter, a cat who has been deemed unadoptable because he's basically the worst cat in the world. Her overbearing persistence in trying to get him adopted leads Dexter to become Dex-Starr, an evil Red Lantern supervillain! Can Jess still find the good in a fuzzy little nemesis who is trying to kill her?

title: Worship
description: When the Fashionistas unveil their new mind controlling perfume, the Powerpuff Girls must find a way to stop them before Townsville falls under their spell.

title: The Perfect Meal
description: KO teams up with Beardo to make the perfect meal for Carol.

title: Cosplay Day
description: Team Tennyson enjoy the biggest convention in town, but when a gawky costume store employee finds a familiar-looking helmet in the back of the store and tries it on, Ben is faced with the return of an old foe in a new form: Forever Knight!

title: Kelsey Quest
description: Kelsey accepts a quest from the Elders of the Creek, but is she ready for her terrifying opponent?

title: El Comienzo de Cobrangutan
description: Mao Mao incita a Cobrangután y a los Piratas del Cielo a convertirse en villanos verdaderamente malvados, dignos de un héroe legendario como él.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: Cuentos de miedo 2
description: Es Halloween de nuevo y la banda trata de contar aterradoras historias a un grupo de niños que piden dulces.

title: Cat Man Do/Impeach Fuzz
description: Cat Man Do: Bubbles saves a seemingly innocent kitty from the clutches of an evil villain. But when the girls discover it's actually the Cat who is evil, they must save the Professor from being the next victim./Impeach Fuzz: When Fuzzy Lumkins throws his hat into the mayoral ring and claims a surprise victory, it's up to the Mayor and the girls to wrestle the office, and the Mayor's actual hat, back from him.

title: Triple T Tigers
description: The Bears meet three cool tiger brothers. Grizz wants to be just like the oldest Tiger, TK, but he may not be the best role model.

title: El Lamento del Krag
description: Cole despierta en una caverna helada donde habita una bestia legendaria, y en su intento por escapar descubre una sorprendente verdad.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Jugo arcoiris
description: Después de desafiarse unos a otros a tomar el Latte de Pegaso de Chef, Izzy y Jude están llenos de energía y Duncan y Courtney hacen un viaje por carretera para tratar de reemplazar la bebida antes de que Chef descubra que desapareció.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: Flyaway
description: When Adorabat's spirit transcends her body during a meditation exercise, Mao Mao and Badgerclops have to figure out a way to return her to the real world.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Side Kicked
description: Zoe builds her own battle suit in hopes of joining Axel's team. The only problem? She can't shrink! Hijinks ensue as a full-sized Zoe tries to assist Axel & co. in a battle against Pyrant and his army of mind-control drones.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Bajo los Reflectores
description: Cuando la reportera Verónica Venegas, madre de Lia, hace un reportaje acerca de Los Fantásticos, Strata El Cazador intenta capturar a Hydorous.

title: Motel
description: Following an insect mishap Clarence's house needs to be fumigated forcing Mary, Chad, and Clarence into a motel. In the meantime, Clarence and Chad learn a bit about responsibility while Mary contemplates a life of letting go.

title: We Are Heroes
description: KO struggles with his upgraded role as a member of the hero team.

title: Karate Mom
description: After surprising Clarence with Martial Arts classes at the "Aberdojo," Mary gets talked into joining the class herself. She loves the slow-paced lessons in discipline and control, but Clarence just wants to have fun and kick butt! Can Mary convince Clarence to stick with the class, earn his belt and have some fun with her?

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Mr. Butt
description: After Starfire is set up by Blackfire and sent to prison, the Titans work to make Blackfire a better sister while Starfire plots her revenge.

title: Don't Read the Comments
description: An obsession with comments and criticisms about him on the Board of Opinions drives Prohyas nuts, affecting Warrior missions for the worse and raising Vambre's ire, I mean, concerns.

title: La Casa del Arbol
description: Vic y Val construyen una casa en el árbol, y Val se libra de Vic con una tarea sin importáncia para construir la casa exactamente como quiere. Pero cuando Vic regresa y trae, sin saberlo, una rama del Árbol Vampiro, la casa del árbol perfecta de Val se convierte en una pesadilla.

title: House
description: Bing is playing "Big Bad Wolf" today with Sula, Coco and Charlie and Bing gets to be the wolf! But what will happen when Bing wants to come into the brick house with everyone else?

title: Ace of Squares
description: Craig vows to make the game of Four Square fun again by challenging its most dominant player!

title: La Ultima Cambia Formas
description: Akita cuenta la historia de "la Elección" y cómo es que ella y su hermano gemelo, Kataru, fueron al bosque para descubrir su forma animal.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Cluckwork Orange
description: After befriending a chicken with a bad attitude at a petting zoo, Jude is followed back to school by the chicken. He defends the bad bird's behavior until he can defend it no longer.

title: Tales from the Omnitrix
description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: The Lonely Haunts Club 2: Doll Island
description: In order to prove their bravery, V&V head to a haunted island to retrieve a special doll, but Charlene and Pineapple are intent on getting it first.

title: Head Chef
description: Mao Mao faces off with Badgerclops in a competition to determine whether cooking (and being a hero) is an art or a science.

title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Avistamiento de Ballenas
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan unirse a un club exclusivo para ver una ballena fuera de lo común.

title: Joyride
description: iEn una venta de artículos usados ​​con el tío Andrew, Axel y Zoe deben evitar que Madcap convierta su juguete tanque perdido, Joyride, en un agente de caos!

title: Secret of the Wolf
description: The Ice Emperor summons an enormous ice Behemoth to attack Lloyd and his faithful wolf companion.

title: Man Person
description: Despite the Titans' protests, Beast Boy becomes convinced that replacing his body parts with robotic limbs makes him more manly.

title: Cambio de Temporada
description: Cuando nuestros héroes regresan de sus vacaciones, K.O. se horroriza al descubrir que las cosas cambiaron.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: The Visitor
description: A vision leads Finn to a friendly civilization and a mysterious crash site.

title: La Comida Perfecta
description: K.O. se alía a Beardo para prepararle la comida perfecta a Carol.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: Rock Show
description: Chad's band Dogmon, plays a show for the first time in years, giving Clarence and Mary a chance to really rock out.

title: Monsterplant
description: Bluster creates a mad scientist's monster from a clump of moss and sends it to scare the Whiffles away. The kindhearted Monsterplant just wants to be friends with them, but the Whiffles are frightened away by how he looks. Share and Dibble work together to show the Whiffles how nice Monsterplant is on the inside.

title: La cita
description: Cuando Chef está feliz ordena pizza para los niños. Esto le da a Owen & Jude la idea de crear una falsa admiradora secreta para Chef.

title: Party Poopers
description: Ben completely ignores Gwen when she takes him to a family fun center. Meanwhile, Frightwig pushes Zombozo back into a life of crime after he ends up becoming a party clown. Now, both Ben and Zombozo will have to learn that you shouldn't ignore your friends!

title: Orangusnake Begins
description: Mao Mao goads Orangusnake and the Sky Pirates into becoming truly terrible villains worthy of a legendary hero such as himself.

title: J-Pony
description: JP decide seguir su corazón y trata de unirse a las Chicas Ecuestres.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: La Parisina
description: Cuando Starfire se obsesiona con una cuchara para servir helado, los demás intentan enseñarle que los objetos inanimados no pueden reemplazar a las personas.

title: Chicken in the Cradle
description: Beast Boy neglects his responsibilities, leaving the other Titans to raise his baby chick.

title: Campeon del Cuadro
description: iCraig promete hacer que el juego de Cuatro Cuadros vuelva a ser divertido cuando desafía a su jugador más experto!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Jail Break
description: Steven teams up with a new ally to rescue the Gems.

title: Jorts
description: When Mr. Gus gets stuck in an embarrassingly super tight pair of jorts, he has to somehow get out of them in order to save his friends.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Afuera Hielo
description: La última creación de Madcap, el Ice Crusher, congela a toda la ciudad, iobligando a Axel y al equipo a enfrentarlo en un juego de hockey de alto riesgo o arriesgarse a caer en otra era de hielo!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Panda's Family
description: While exploring a lantern festival, the Bears encounter Panda's long-lost family.

title: Continue?
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman hires the Warriors to retrieve the Orb of Sphericity from a temple in Galacton. The odd thing is, this temple has save points! When the Warriors are defeated, they respawn, but Vambre remembers what happened and Prohyas does not.

title: #GatoRabioso
description: Jessica Cruz está convencida de que puede conseguirle un hogar definitivo perfecto para Dexter, un gato que la gente considera inadoptable porque, básicamente, es el peor gato del mundo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Espero que esto vuele
description: Rad intenta mejorar su camioneta y hacerla volar.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Grilled Cheese Deluxe
description: Mordecai and Rigby lie about being astronauts in order to cut in line at a restaurant.

title: Ventila-hala
description: Chef le confisca la mega-bola a Owen y la guarda en su oficina. Duncan, viendo una oportunidad para conseguir ayuda escapando de la guardaería, lidera un equipo de fuga por los conductos del aire acondicionado para recuperarla.

title: Ben sin fondo
description: Los Tennyson se topan con un "pozo sin fondo": un pozo formado naturalmente, que carece de fondo. Ben se debate internamente si debe entrar o no, ihasta que llega Kevin 11 y empieza a incitarlo a hacer una carrera hacia abajo!

title: Free Cake
description: Mordecai and Rigby throw Skips a surprise birthday party in order to get free cake.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Locked Out
description: When Uncle Grandpa gets locked out of his RV and accidentally sets off the security system, it's up to him and his friends to disarm it before it destroys them.

title: The Castle
description: When Mom is away "anything goes" and Dad's lack of rules soon attracts unwelcome houseguests.

title: Death Punchies
description: Rigby learns an ultimate karate move and becomes the bully of the park.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: The Breathtaking Bolly Show
description: If Mush-Mush had Bolly's speed, he'd want everyone to see just how awesomely fast he was. But Bolly is different - he just likes to use his speed helping Mushables. So when Mush-Mush organizes a big stunt for Bolly, he refuses. He just doesn't like to show off. But Mush-Mush promised everyone a show so a show he will give them with Mush-Mush performing instead of Bolly! Gulp!

title: #TheGoodTheBadAndTheBizarre
description: Everything is going well for Kara Danvers, both as a teen and a superhero, until she starts taking the blame for things she didn't do, and the emergence of a new supervillain threatens to destroy Supergirl's hard-earned reputation.

title: El Trampolin de Hamburguesa
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben encontrar una manera de usar el trampolín de Hamburguesa sin que él se sienta usado.

title: Plundsmas
description:
The Mutants refuse to celebrate their favorite holiday, Plunds-Mas, now that Plun-Darr is gone. So now it's up to the Thundercats to raise their spirits by enacting the
eight horrors of Plunds-Mas!

title: Dia de cosplay
description: El Equipo Tennyson está disfrutando la mejor convención de la ciudad. Pero cuando un empleado torpe de una tienda de disfraces encuentra un casco de aspecto familiar en el fondo de la tienda y se lo prueba, Ben debe enfrentar el regreso de un viejo enemigo en una nueva forma: iel Caballero Eterno!

title: Que Ocurre con Dan
description: Cuando Dan se comporta de forma extraña con los Fantásticos, Lightning olfatea la verdad: iUn impostor!

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Doorway to Helen
description: Craig makes a long distance connection with a kid that loves the creek as much as he does.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Suelta
description: Cuando el espíritu de Adorabat trasciende su cuerpo durante un ejercicio de meditación, Mao Mao y Colosal tienen que descubrir un modo de devolverla al mundo real.

title: Guess What?
description: Pocoyo plays a game with us. He shows us a series of different extremely strange shapes and wants us to guess what they are. A fun guessing game, learning to look at things in different ways...

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Pirates
description: When Aqualad and Raven fall for each other, Beast Boy fights this match - with intensity.

title: El Arbol del Viajero
description: Carcomido por la culpa por haber perdido el Té del Viajero, cole se embarca en un peligrosa misión haciala cima de una montaña esperando encontrar el legendario Árbol del Viajero, que se supone que está custodiado por una feroz bestia.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Truth
description: An old Plumber partner of Max's resurfaces with nefarious intentions and ends up stealing the dangerous Null Void Projector.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Perdidas y Ganancias
description: Un promotor llamado Everett Ray quiere convencer a Los Fantásticos de ingresar a una liga oficial de Batallas Bakugan.

title: Just Another Manic Mojo/Mime for a Change
description: Just Another Manic Mojo: The Powerpuff Girls lose their baseball in Mojo's house, offering him the perfect opportunity to destroy these pesky superheroines if he can only get them to sit still./Mime for a Change: An accidental bleach spill turns Rainbow the Clown into the malevolent Mr. Mime. He proceeds to turn Townsville black and white and dead all over.

title: Upside Down
description: Pato gets stuck hanging upside down from the sky. Pocoyo and the friends try to help him down.

title: The Scoop
description: The Titans find it odd when Starfire becomes friends with an ice cream scoop.

title: Bubblevicious/The Bare Facts
description: Bubblevicious: Bubbles is tired of people dismissing her as more sugar than spice. When she sets out to prove she's hardcore, she takes everyone by surprise, even Mojo Jojo./The Bare Facts: After Mojo kidnaps and blindfolds him, the Mayor has to rely on the girls' very different individual accounts of the crime to figure out exactly what happened.

title: Super Sweet 6
description: Morbucks throws the biggest birthday party of all time, and Blossom is the only one not invited.

title: Leg Wrestler
description: When Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus argue over what show to watch on TV, Pizza Steve has the perfect way to solve their dilemma: Leg wrestling battle!

title: Dizzy
description: Bing wants to do spinning on the spinny chair so Pando pushes him superfast. But what will happen when Bing starts to feel too dizzy and wants to stop?

title: Tree Buds
description: Vic and Val build a treehouse and Val dismisses Vic with a frivolous task so he can build the treehouse exactly how he wants. But when Vic returns unknowingly with a branch from El Arbol Vampiro, Val's perfect treehouse turns into a nightmare!

title: El Club Salchicha
description: Perricornio está decidido a convertirse en el rey de los hot dogs y se une al Club Salchicha, una competencia clandestina de comer hot dogs.

title: The Last of the Formlings
description: Akita tells the story of the "Choosing" and how she, and her twin brother, Kataru, went into the wilds to discover their animal forms.

title: Magnet Madness/Caillou the Dinosaur Hunter/Caillou the Astronaut
description: Caillou is playing with the fridge magnets and learns lots of things about them./The whole family goes on a trip to the natural history museum to look at the dinosaurs./Caillou wants to play with both his friends Clementine and Xavier at the playschool playground.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Jake the Dad
description: Jake's a daddy, but being a father and keeping his rainicorn pups from killing themselves or each other is a lot harder than he imagined.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: JPony
description: JP decides to follow his heart and tries to join the Horse Girls.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Mr Big Duck
description: Pato is enjoying playing at being very grown up and doesn't want to join in the games with his friends. Eventually though, Pato and the others realize that playing with friends is much more fun than hanging around being 'cool'.

title: Joshua & Margaret Investigations
description: Finn and Jake's parents hunt an unearthly menace in the woods.

title: Work Like a Charm
description: Chep becomes obsessed with learning all about Mushlore - all the funny little traditions and things that Mushables believe in. Morel is the expert in Mushlore so Chep becomes his apprentice. But the more Chep discovers about Mushlore the more he becomes a true believer to the point that it becomes quite dangerous!

title: The Cave of Gelatinous Doom!
description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

title: The Comet
description: Finn, Jake and Orgalorg converge with the comet and meet their destiny.

title: #BackInAFlash
description: After an embarrassing incident ruins Barbara Gordon's reputation, rather than owning it and moving on, she decides it's easier to harness The Flash's newly discovered ability to travel back in time and alter the delicate fabric of the space-time continuum.

title: Surprise Machine
description: Bing and Sula are in Padget's Shop today when they discover the new surprise machine. But what will happen when Bing's surprise toy isn't the one he was hoping for?

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Boo
description: Lucas loves to give his friends a scare on Halloween.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Venthalla
description: Owen has his super ball confiscated and locked up in Chef's office. Duncan, seeing an opportunity to get help escaping the daycare, leads an away team into the vents to recover Owen's ball.

title: Enredos Perrunos
description: Lightning descubre un nuevo Bakugan, Artulean, y eso desata una fuerte rivalidad entre él y Howlkor.

title: The Traveler's Tree
description: Guilt-ridden over having lost the Traveler's Tea, Cole embarks on a dangerous quest to the top of a nearby mountain in hopes of finding the legendary Traveler's Tree - a tree which is supposedly guarded by a fearsome beast.

title: Krag's Lament
description: Cole awakens inside an icy cavern belonging to a legendary beast, and attempts to escape, only to discover a surprising truth.

title: El pollo maniaco
description: Después de hacerse amigo de un pollo con mala actitud en un zoológico de contacto, este lo sigue de regreso a la escuela. Él defiende la mala conducta del ave hasta que ya no puede seguir haciéndolo.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Mi Enemigo, Mi Amigo
description: El terrible Dragón de Hielo del Emperador ataca de nuevo, arrasando la aldea de los Pescadores de Hielo, obligando a los ninjas a seguir los pasos de Lloyd.

title: Sr. Luna
description: Wynton encuentra un nuevo Bakugan que resulta difícil de controlar, y las cosas se complican cuando el Coronel Tripp se apodera de Trox.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Captured Clops
description: Badgerclops is tired of his responsibilities at Sheriff's HQ, so he joins the Sky Pirates.

title: The Best Team
description: When Madcap and his minions crash a soapbox derby, the team must stop the baddies and help Axel - stuck in a car with Luka - cross the finish line!

title: Iced Out
description: Madcap's latest creation, the Ice Crusher, puts the whole city in a deep freeze, forcing Axel and the team to face him in a game of high-stakes hockey or risk slip-sliding into another ice age!

title: La Captura de Colosal
description: Colosal se cansa de sus responsabilidades en el cuartel general de sheriff y decide unirse a los Piratas del Cielo.

title: They Sent Us a Pie/Dust in the Wind
description: A giant pie is sent to Pretty Big City to stop an asteroid… but the Mechas and friends have eaten the whole thing!/The Singing Stone Heads are ready to perform at the Museum, but when they open their mouths, they sneeze instead of sing!

title: Entrega especial
description: Después de ser interrumpida por Bim Bom durante su canción matutina, una furiosa Unikitty sigue el consejo de sus amigos y escribe sus sentimientos en una carta con la intención de quedársela, pero la envía accidentalmente. La banda sale en una salvaje persecución de los servicios postales del Unireino para evitar que la irrespetuosa carta llegue a Bim Bom y hiera sus sentimientos.

title: Free Chili
description: When Owen hides a walkie-talkie inside his chili dog, Harold believes it's an alien here to destroy Earth.

title: Wiener Club
description: Puppycorn is determined to become the Hot Dog King and joins an underground hot dog eating contest called Weiner Club. Rick warns "you are what you eat," but Puppycorn doesn't listen and eats so many hot dogs he becomes the new champion of Weiner Club. Unfortunately he also literally turns into a hot dog, that the other club members reveal they are going to eat! Unikitty and the gang now must attack with vegetables and defeat the hot dog-eating baddies in order to save the giant hot-dog-shaped Puppycorn and turn him back to normal.

title: Caillou Plays the Drums/Caillou's Marching Band/Caillou Sings
description: Clementine's big brother Billy has a new drum set and is having lots of fun playing as loud as he can./Caillou and his friends are very excited when a real marching band goes by the playschool./The playschool is having a talent show and Caillou wants to sing a song.

title: #SobrecargaElectrica
description: Cuando creen que Supergirl ha muerto en una batalla con Livewire, Kara Danvers decide reinventarse con una nueva apariencia, una nueva personalidad y un nuevo nombre: iPower Girl!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Rowdy Ruff Boys
description: Mojo Jojo creates the ultimate weapons against the Powerpuff Girls, boy equivalents! Enter Butch, Boomer and Brick, The Rowdyruff Boys.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Manzana Mandona
description: Manzana queda a cargo de la Tienda de Dolar por primera vez.

title: #ScrambledEggs
description: It's egg-xactly what you think: the home economics "Egg-Baby" assignment, where students are paired up and given an egg to "care for" over a weekend. But when tragedy befalls egg after egg, what should be an easy assignment escalates into a madcap romp with super-high stakes!

title: Mandora Saves Christmas
description: Santa Claus is on the run from Mandora! Can the Thundercats help him get off Third Earth without getting caught? And can Santa Claus teach them a little something about this weird new holiday "Christmas"?

title: El Club de Los Solitarios 2, La Isla de las Munecas
description: Para probar su valentía, Victor y Valentino se dirigen a una isla embrujada para recuperar una muñeca especial, pero Charlene y Piña están decididos a obtenerla antes que ellos.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: Caffeinated Concert Tickets
description: Mordecai & Rigby make a deal with a Coffee Bean to help them stay awake to work major overtime to pay for concert tickets.

title: The Date
description: When Chef is happy he orders pizza for the kids, this gives Owen & Jude the idea to create a fake secret admirer for Chef.

title: Squideo Games
description: When Vambre and Prohyas are hired for separate gigs, they end up having to battle each other to claim a rare Squideo from Lake Sprite in Galacton.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Una Verdad a Medias
description: Un críptico correo electrónico lleva a Los Fantásticos en busca de un Bakugan desaparecido, pero pronto se dan cuenta de que el correo era una prueba de un misterioso benefactor.

title: Eggsellent Adventure
description: Thomas and Percy have a difficult delivery - getting eggs and other cake ingredients safely to Vicarstown for their bake-off.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: The Knights
description: Gumball and Tobias compete for Penny's affection by putting on the lamest duel in history.

title: Neon Beach Party
description: Bluster and his Bad Crowd arrive at a lakeside beach for his summer vacation, unaware that the Care Bears are having their vacation on the opposite shore. Trapped inside Bluster's climate-control dome and forced to spend their vacations together, the Bears must find a way to make friends with their ill-tempered neighbors.

title: Snowflakes/Caillou Shoots! He Scores!/Caillou goes Tobogganing
description: Caillou eagerly awaits the first snowfall of winter, and imagines himself building the biggest snowman./Caillou wants to play hockey with Billy and the other big kids./Mommy can't find Caillou's toboggan for the playschool tobogganing trip.

title: Cupcake Job
description: When the Bears' beloved laptop breaks, they finally have the need to do something they've never done before: get jobs. Working at a trendy cupcake shop, the Bears find  that the working world is much tougher than they realized.

title: Moustache Cream
description: When UG and the gang are in a rush to purchase some emergency moustache cream, they face a formidable foe: Mart Mart.

title: Lil' Squid
description: The Baby Bears build a submarine and explore the depths of an aquarium so they can bring a lost squid to its family.

title: Band Together
description: The babies learn about music and improvise their own orchestra.

title: Trapped in the Tower
description: During a fun fireworks show, Unikitty and Master Frown become trapped in the horn of the Unikitty Castle when she catches Master Frown messing with her fireworks. Unikitty takes this as an opportunity to figure out why Master Frown is always such a Cranky McCrabby Face all the time, if only Master Frown would let his emotional guard down! She tries all kinds of tactics, a song, a dance, even a firework with a face drawn on it named "Professor Pow Pow, licensed therapist" Getting nowhere, Unikitty ends up raging out and setting the tower and all the fireworks alight. In desperation to not burn alive, Master Frown tells Unikitty a story about a younger Master Frown who was gifted a special lollipop but after a freak chain of events, was broken right before his eyes. Unikitty cries her eyes out and puts out the fires and then reveals it was her plan all along to get Master Frown to talk about his feelings!

title: Mascara de Poder
description: Philomena Dusk, de la Corporación AAAnimus, contrata a Magnus y le implanta un dispositivo que aumenta el poder de su Bakugan para derrotar a Dan.

title: Dales aire y dejalos salir
description: En la granja eólica de Mojave, Gwen y Max intentan enderezar las locas ideas de Ben sobre como funciona el viento. Pero cuando encuentran a los Climáticos usando las imponentes turbinas para sus viles objetivos, ¿podrá Ben aceptar los hechos a tiempo para derrotarlos?

title: Rock Porcupunk
description: Madcap recurre a Axel y su equipo en busca de ayuda después de que una actualización sónica a Porcupunk amenaza con derribar la casa.

title: Aguafiestas
description: Ben ignora completamente a Gwen cuando van a un centro de diversión familiar. Mientras tanto, Frightwig empuja a Zombozo a una vida de crímenes luego de que este termina convertido en un payaso para fiestas. iAhora, Zombozo y Ben deben aprender que no deberías ignorar a tus amigos!

title: Calliope Crack-Up
description: When the engines are delivering attractions to the annual Harwick Beach Carnival, a series of mistakes causes the precious Calliope to break. Luckily, the engines come up with a creative solution.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Authority
description: Granny JoJo's overprotective behavior puts the Wattersons in danger...from themselves.

title: Burger's Trampoline
description: After learning that Burger has a trampoline, Apple and Onion pay him a visit. Burger thinks they came especially to see him and is overjoyed.

title: Evil's Encore
description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

title: Wind Some, Lose Some
description: At the Mojave Wind Farm in Texas, Max and Gwen plan to set Ben straight on his kooky ideas about how wind works, but when they find the Weatherheads using the towering turbines for their latest nefarious plan, will Ben face facts in time to blow them away?

title: Apple's in Charge
description: Apple is put in charge of the Dollar Store for the very first time.

title: Bottomless Ben
description: While visiting Carlsbad Caverns National Park, the Tennyson's come across the "Bottomless Pit", a naturally formed pit with no bottom. Ben fights his better judgment to jump in the pit and be the first person to find the bottom, until Kevin 11 shows up and starts to goad Ben into a contest to the bottom of the pit! The natural rivalry is put on hold, however, with the arrival of Breaker One-Nine, who has come to destroy the Caverns!

title: Blossom3
description: After being blasted by Duplikate, Blossom turns into a triple threat.

title: Never Boop a Robot
description: When Lucas boops a robot, he and his friends are chased around House!

title: Keeping It Together
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems revisit the Kindergarten and find a dark secret.

title: Bobbie no Blobbie
description: Axel descubre que el culpable del traje mecánico perdido de Bobbie Blobby es Masko, que solo quería limpiar sus cañones de arcilla obstruidos, pero deja que el traje caiga en las manos (o tentáculos) del Dr. Nautilus, icon la intención de inundar las alcantarillas!

title: Grizzly the Movie
description: Grizz gets cast in a movie about a Grizzly Bear! But Grizz soon realizes the movie's depiction of grizzly bears is not what he had in mind.

title: #PowerSurge
description: When Supergirl is presumed dead after a battle with Livewire, Kara Danvers decides to reinvent herself with a new look, a new personality, and a new name, Power Girl.

title: Special Delivery
description: After being rudely interrupted by Bim Bom during her daily morning song, an angry Unikitty takes the advice of her friends and writes down her feelings into a letter with the intention of keeping the letter to herself, but then accidentally sends it off, complete with postage! The gang then goes on a wild chase through the Unikingdom mail delivery service to keep that rude letter from getting into the hands of Bim Bom, and ultimately hurting her feelings. Turns out, Unikitty's "rude" is everyone else's "nice" and the letter was full of compliments.

title: #HuevosRevueltos
description: Gracias a la tarea de la clase de Economía Domestica, los estudiantes son emparejados y se les entrega un huevo para "cuidar" durante el fin de semana. Pero cuando la tragedia acontece huevo tras huevo, lo que debería ser una tarea fácil, ise convierte en una disparatada persecución!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: #LaBuenaLaMalaYLaBizarra
description: Las cosas van bien en la vida de Kara Danvers, como adolescente y como superheroína, hasta que comienza a hacerse responsable de cosas que no hizo y la aparición de un nuevo supervillano amenaza con destruir la reputación que tanto le costó ganar a Supergirl.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: La aventura de Kelsey
description: Kelsey acepta una misión de los Ancianos del Arroyo, pero ¿está lista para su aterrador rival?
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Baila Reynaldo Baila
description: Vic está desesperado por ganar el premio en efectivo para el concurso de baile en Monte Macabro y está frustrado porque Val, su pareja, no le deja tomar todas las decisiones. Por eso, elige un compañero diferente: Reynaldo. Pero Vic presiona demasiado a Reynaldo para hacer realidad su visión artística. Al final, Vic aprende que, para tener éxito, hay que ser socios en igualdad de condiciones.

title: Hurricane Dilliss
description: Things in the Wendle household are turned upside down when Mary's mom Dyllis comes to visit, butting her way into every corner of Clarence, Mary and Chad's life.

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: We Need to Talk
description: Greg tells Steven and Connie the story of how he learned about Gem fusion.

title: Business as Unusual
description: Bugs and Daffy open competing lemonade stands.

title: Band of Friends
description: Pocoyo meets a funny little red shape. At first it teases and hides from him, making him jump and chasing him around. But then it brings along its friends and together they put on a music and dancing show for Pocoyo and his gang.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Seasons Change
description: When our heroes return from time off, KO is horrified to discover that things have changed.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Framed
description: Kevin 11 is back and out for revenge. And with the ability to shape-shift into several of Ben's alien heroes, he's been framing Ben for his crimes.

title: Fiebre de la Baya de Azúcar
description: Mao Mao intenta ocultar su amor por el pastel de fruta.

title: Don
description: Rigby's estranged accountant brother comes back to help save the park from an audit. While everyone loves Don, Rigby wants nothing to do with him.

title: The Harder They Fall
description: Bugs is embarrassed to admit he doesn't know how to skate.

title: El Pollo en La Cuna
description: Chico Bestia debe aprender a dejar de lado sus costumbres de andar de fiesta para criar a su pollito.

title: Food Around the Corner
description: Ben as Gravattack attempts to moderate a fragile peace treaty, but must endure the attacks of tiny alien fleas, which have inhabited his body.

title: Killing Time
description: Mumm-Ra, the Ever-Living decides he'll nap for a thousand years, till the Thundercats are long gone. But when he wakes up, he's shocked to discover that Third Earth is even more in love with them than ever.

title: The First Thundsgiving
description: Tygra is furious after the other Thundercats eat the last of his Thunderian ingredients. To make it up to him they go hunting for substitutes on Third Earth to show him the food on their new planet is just as delicious as the food they had back on their old home.

title: Jefe de Cocina
description: Mao Mao se enfrenta a Colosal en una competencia para determinar si cocinar (y ser un héroe) es un arte o una ciencia.

title: The Last Kid in the Creek
description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

title: Regurgitated Reminiscence
description: Elliott and Mo go to great lengths to retrieve Frankie's old coffee machine.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Chille Tid
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems try to relax with a slumber party.

title: Sugar Berry Fever
description: Mao Mao tries to hide his love of cobbler.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Chaotic Clumping
description: Elliott and Mo accidentally take a teleporter together, and find themselves closer than they've ever been before. Will they decide to mutually part ways?

title: A Very Special Episode
description: Rainbow Quartz 2.0 promised to hang out with Onion the same day Sunstone scheduled a home safety Geminar! How can Steven be in two places, and two fusions, at once?

title: Baby Boi TP
description: Apple and Onion run out of toilet paper because Apple's been building a huge modern art sculpture with it. They're going to need more if Apple is to finish and Onion is to be able to resume his normal toilet activities.

title: Tutores Bakugan
description: Dan y Wynton conocen a un extraño chico que los lleva a un laberinto subterráneo, donde descubren que el Bakugan del chico ha sido esclavizado.

title: A Star is Blossom
description: When Bubbles gets the lead in the school play, Blossom's jealousy consumes her.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: Whale Spotting
description: In order to see a rare whale, Apple and Onion have to become members of an exclusive club, but one of them doesn't quite have the chops.

title: El Equipo Exit
description: Los Fantásticos compiten por el número de visitas en sus videos con un equipo rival llamado "El equipo Exit" en una batalla donde se juegan el todo por el todo.

title: Dance Reynaldo Dance
description: Vic is desperate to win the cash prize for the dance contest in Monte Macabre and is frustrated that his partner Val won't let him call all the shots. Instead he chooses a different partner: Reynaldo. But Vic pushes Reynaldo too hard to execute his artistic vision. Eventually he learns that in order to be a success, you have to be equal partners.

title: Reunion en la Oscuridad
description: Axel debe ayudar a Bearbarian a superar su miedo secreto a la oscuridad para evitar que Dynamo le robe su viaje.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Mr. McStuffles
description: Daffy doesn't want to give up his old toy, even after he's outgrown it.

title: Internet Troll
description: Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus venture into cyberspace to defeat an Internet troll.

title: Grudge Match
description: Ben and Kevin 11 are beamed up to a space ship where must learn to battle together in order to bring down a vicious alien fight promoter.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: Una Necesidad Inquietante
description: La aparición de un nuevo campo Bakugan hace que los chicos del pueblo corran a buscar a sus propios Bakugan. Pero cuando el campo es contaminado, Lia debe salvarlos a todos.

title: Jump Scare
description: When Victor starts to feel left out because Valentino and Isabella are hanging out without him, he becomes determined get the trio's old dynamic back, even if it means souring their relationship!

title: Hibernation
description: The bears, being an urban bunch, hadn't ever heard of the idea of hibernation until Chloe tells them about it. Grizz, loving the idea of eating a ton and then just sleeping to his heart's content, goes for it with reckless abandon.  But Grizz is so excited for hibernating... that he can't fall asleep.

title: El Secreto del Lobo
description: El Emperador de Hielo despierta a una bestia gigante para que ataquea Lloyd y a su fiel compañero.

title: Duck Duck Juice
description: After daring each other to drink Chef's Pegasus Rainbow Latte, Izzy and Jude are jacked up like crazy and Duncan and Courtney take a road trip to try and replace the drink before Chef finds out it's gone.

title: War of the Weirds
description: Marvin the Martian comes to visit, and the babies learn to accept differences.

title: The Outside
description: The family goes to visit Richard's Dad. Based on his basic living standards and extended absence from Richard's life, they assume Frankie must have done a stretch in the slammer. When Frankie comes to stay with the Wattersons, they decide the way to make him comfortable is to make him uncomfortable and turn their house into a prison.

title: Historias del Omnitrix
description: El Equipo Tennyson comparte historias de fogón en un episodio estilo antología, que enfrenta a Ben contra Kevin 11, su archirrival, y le enseña el poder de la imaginación a nuestro héroe.

title: Lord Cowboy Darrell
description: Everyone is forced to deal with some major changes at Boxmore.

title: Atrapados en la torre
description: Durante un divertido espectáculo de fuegos artificiales, Unikitty y Master Frown quedan atrapados en el cuerno del castillo luego de que ella lo sorprende tratando de arruinar sus fuegos artificiales.

title: Hope This Flies
description: Rad attempts to upgrade his van and make it fly.

title: Ice Lolly
description: It's hot today so Bing and Flop are having yummy delicious ice pops from Gilly. But what will happen to their ice pops when Bing and Flop are rescuing Froggy from the swimming pool in the garden?

title: Dinner Party
description: When Clarence's mom takes Clarence to a stuffy dinner party, Clarence embarks on a quest for fun wherever it can be found.

title: Rising Tides, Crashing Skies
description: Ronaldo does some investigative reporting on whether Steven and the Crystal Gems are safe for Beach City.

title: Heatwave
description: Apple and Onion try to spread cheer during a city-wide heatwave.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Chile libre
description: Cuando Owen oculta un walkie talky dentro de su perro con chile, Harold cree que es un alienígena que vino a destruir la tierra.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Uh, Oh, Dynamo
description: Worried about his little girls' safety, the Professor creates Powerpuff Dynamo, a state-of-the-art protection system, to help them in battle.

title: Jakesuit
description: Jake is sick and tired of Finn using his body as a suit of armor so he convinces Finn to trade places to show him how much it really stinks.

title: Lord Vaquero Darrell
description: Todos se ven obligados a enfrentar grandes cambios en Boxmore.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Ola de Calor
description: Manzana y Cebollín tratan de esparcir alegría durante una ola de calor en toda la ciudad.

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Papel de Bano Bebecin
description: Manzana necesita conseguir la provisión del papel higiénico que usaría en toda su vida para terminar su escultura de arte moderno.

title: Grizz Helps
description: When his brothers don't need his help for the day, Grizz leaves the cave to assist anyone he can throughout the city.

title: Show and Tell/Caillou the Magician/Caillou's Castle
description: Caillou has to decide on a nice surprise to bring to playschool for Show and Tell./Grandma shows Caillou a simple magic trick, which makes him decide to be a magician./Caillou wants to play castles and dragons, even though Gilbert isn't very keen on playing the dragon.

title: An Evening with Mic and Hun
description: Using their tickets to spend an "Evening with Mic & Hun" to get out of having dinner with Chata's comadres, Victor and Valentino get more than they bargained for, a terrifying dinner party game where losing means a permanent stay in the Underworld!

title: Grune
description: The ThunderCats face the greatest threat of their lives: Grune the Destroyer! He's the ghost of an evil ThunderCat and he wants revenge! How are They Gonna Beat Grune??? You'll have to watch the episode!

title: Caillou of the Antarctic/Deep Sea Caillou/Caillou in the Bayou
description: Caillou is playing with Jeffrey and Jason when he gets accidentally pushed down./There's a new girl named Lee Wun in playschool, but she's so shy she won't talk to anybody./The whole family is on the way to the beach but accidentally ends up on a trail through a swamp.
